### **3. Aggressive Push Notifications (Loss Aversion + FOMO)**
**Goal:** **Trigger fear of missing out** and **loss aversion**.

#### **Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) Example**
```javascript
// Send a push notification with FOMO messaging
function sendFomoPushNotification(userId) {
  const message = {
    notification: {
      title: "⏳ Your streak is ending!",
      body: "Come back in the next hour or lose your 3-day streak!",
      icon: "https://your-app.com/streak-icon.png"
    },
    data: {
      click_action: "open_streak_recovery"
    },
    token: userId // Replace with actual user token
  };

  admin.messaging().send(message)
    .then((response) => {
      console.log("FOMO push sent:", response);
    })
    .catch((error) => {
      console.error("Error sending FOMO push:", error);
    });
}
```

#### **Push Notification Copy (Test These)**
1. **"🚨 Your streak is ending in 1 hour—come back now!"**
2. **"🔥 Only 3 spots left in this group—claim yours!"**
3. **"⏰ This deal expires in 2 hours—don’t wait!"**
4. **"💀 You’re missing out on [X]—check it out!"**
5. **"🎁 You unlocked a rare reward—open it now!"**

