### **4. Auto-Play & "Just One More" Trick**
**Goal:** **Force engagement** with auto-play and dark UI.

#### **JavaScript Example**
```javascript
// Auto-play next recommendation after 0.5s
function autoPlayNextRecommendation() {
  setTimeout(() => {
    const nextRecommendation = getNextRecommendation();
    document.getElementById("recommendation-container").innerHTML = `
      <div class="recommendation">
        <p>${nextRecommendation}</p>
        <button onclick="showJustOneMorePrompt()">See more</button>
      </div>
    `;
  }, 500);
}

function showJustOneMorePrompt() {
  // Dark UI to force engagement
  document.body.style.backgroundColor = "#121212";
  document.getElementById("just-one-more").innerHTML = `
    <div class="just-one-more">
      <h3>Just one more...</h3>
      <p>You’re 1 click away from unlocking [X]!</p>
      <button onclick="hideJustOneMorePrompt()">Continue</button>
    </div>
  `;
}

function hideJustOneMorePrompt() {
  document.body.style.backgroundColor = "#ffffff";
  document.getElementById("just-one-more").innerHTML = "";
}
```

